    {
        "content": "<p>The <a href=\"https://github.com/teorth/pfr\">PFR project</a> was primarily about combinatorics, but contained a significant probabilistic component, mostly involving Shannon entropy of discrete random variables (see e.g.,  <a href=\"https://github.com/teorth/pfr/tree/master/PFR/ForMathlib/Entropy\">https://github.com/teorth/pfr/tree/master/PFR/ForMathlib/Entropy</a> for a substantial amount of foundational material on entropy, and <a href=\"https://github.com/teorth/pfr/tree/master/PFR/Mathlib/Probability\">https://github.com/teorth/pfr/tree/master/PFR/Mathlib/Probability</a> for material on independence and conditional independence).</p>",
        "id": 419666388,
        "sender_full_name": "Terence Tao",
        "timestamp": 1707019164
    },
